Package: scalexptest
Title: Statistical Tests for the Scale-Exponential Family of Distributions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Parsa", "Hosseinipour Rafsanjani", , "parsahosseini2001@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Performs hypothesis tests for the scale-exponential family of
    distributions, which includes Exponential, Gamma and Weibull among
    others. This package provides functions to calculate critical values,
    determine rejection regions, and compute test power to support
    statistical inference.
License: use_gpl3_license()
URL: https://github.com/phrafsanjani/scalexptest
BugReports: https://github.com/phrafsanjani/scalexptest/issues
Imports:
    expint,
    pracma
Encoding: UTF-8
